        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+2 greater striking holy shifting morningstar* has a head that appears to be a deep crimson metal rose with thorny petals. When you activate a *thorn brush* to Shift Weapon, you can cause it to take the shape of a painter\u2019s brush. While in this shape, it can\u2019t be used as a weapon (it can still be activated to Shift Weapon back into a morningstar), but it does grant a +2 item bonus to Crafting checks to paint or otherwise use the tool while creating artwork.",
        "level": 15,
